<p><strong>Fast Healing (Sp)</strong> An inquisitor troop's fast healing is a reflection of the fact that each round, some of the inquisitors in the troop cast cure light wounds spells on wounded members. Not all inquisitors in a troop use this ability simultaneously, and they can only grant fast healing to the troop for up to 10 rounds per day. Activating this ability is a free action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity.</p>
